high_descs: Walk toward the fridge and then turn to the long white kitchen island and approach it.
Pick up the spoon from the center of the island.
Walk to the right toward the sink and then take the spoon to the stove on your left.
Place the spoon on the pan.
Pick up the pan and spoon that are on the stove.
Head back to your right, toward the sink.
Place the pan and spoon into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a spoon in a pan into the sink.

high_descs: turn to face kitchen island
pick up spoon from island
walk to face stove
put spoon onto plate on front left burner on stove
pick up plate from stove
walk to face sink
put plate in the sink
anns.task_desc: put plate and spoon in sink

high_descs: Move forward, pass the stool and face the table on your left.
Pick up the spoon on the table, left of the tomato.
Bring the spoon to the stove on the other side of the table.
Put the spoon on the pan on the stove.
Pick up the pan with spoon on the stove.
Turn around, bring the pan with spoon to the sink on your left.
Put the pan with spoon in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with spoon in the sink.
